---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Manifesto | ForgeCore" description="ForgeCore is building a resilient financial instrument, not a trend product.">
  <section class="section">
    <div class="reading">
      <p class="eyebrow">Manifesto</p>
      <h1>ForgeCore is building a resilient financial instrument, not a trend product.</h1>
      <div class="prose">
        <p>ForgeCore exists to discover opportunity, create real assets, deploy monetization, measure outcomes, and adapt without emotional drift.</p>
        <p>It is not a chatbot. It is not a script. It is not a content farm wearing AI language. It is a long-term revenue system built for resilience.</p>
        <p>The system treats models as labor and architecture as the source of control. It does not chase novelty for its own sake. It does not expand without validation. It values proof over claims, structure over noise, and compounding over flash.</p>
        <p>If a platform changes, ForgeCore adapts. If a channel weakens, ForgeCore reallocates. If a strategy underperforms, ForgeCore prunes it. The goal is strategic autonomy, not dependency on temporary conditions.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
